{"tid":983800,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"[PC/IOS/AN]三國殺online集中討論區 [1]","createTime":"2019-01-16T09:25:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-11T10:45:19.000Z","uid":153976,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"c0612158e15d7ffd67c530d7c0298b1427686fd8","tid":983800,"uid":153976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-16T09:25:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TdXQWuc.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTdXQWuc.png&h=e411da6d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n三國殺是遊卡推出的一款風靡全球的以三國為背景的策略卡牌桌遊，經典國戰玩法，百萬名將任由你搭配，楚雄爭霸，等你決戰沙場！<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.sanguosha.com/Home\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.sanguosha.com%2FHome&d=us0DE1UdPinnP7OaCz4lkEkviAvgRC9mxyv2vFgVDqU%3D&h=faae9654\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.sanguosha.com/Home</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong>標準版武將</strong><br />\n三國殺經典武將包，包含魏、蜀、吳、群四方勢力，共26名武將。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>神話再臨</strong><br />\n神話再臨系列是三國殺的一個武將擴展包，取《孫子兵法&middot;軍爭》中的&ldquo;故其疾如風，其徐如林，侵掠如火，不動如山，難知如陰，動如雷震。&rdquo;分為六個擴展包。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>一將成名</strong><br />\n三國殺武將設計大賽，由廣大熱愛桌遊、熱愛三國文化、熱愛三國殺的動漫畫手、設計人員一起設計的武將。包括一將成名2011、2012、2013、2014、2015五個擴展包。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>星火燎原</strong><br />\n三國殺十週年全新擴展包，取《三國演義》第六十九回&ldquo;北斗主死，南斗主生。&rdquo;其中南斗六星分別為天府星、天梁星、天機星、天同星、天相星、七殺星六個擴展包。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>国战</strong><br />\n魏蜀吳群，雙將配合，為國而戰。分為標準包、陣包、勢包共計76名武將。"},{"pid":"cf58942e815878f096d33d1e230ed1fd93dd457c","tid":983800,"uid":153976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-16T09:25:22.000Z","msg":"有冇巴打有玩三國殺online"},{"pid":"ce926d76c78938ca91afbbbec121417d7e699854","tid":983800,"uid":153976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-16T09:29:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"21c38bd2ef3f382248c91cf43facbd1363d2fccb","tid":983800,"uid":142878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-16T09:31:21.000Z","msg":"online